{{!< layouts/main}}

<h2>New Team Created</h2>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>A new team has been created in the Incubation Management System.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <h3>Team Details:</h3>
  <p><strong>Team Name:</strong> {{teamName}}</p>
  {{#if companyName}}
  <p><strong>Company Name:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
  <p><strong>Created:</strong> {{createdDate}}</p>
</div>

{{#if teamLeaderName}}
<div style="background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;">
  <p><strong>Team Leader:</strong> {{teamLeaderName}} ({{teamLeaderEmail}})</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>The team is now active in the system. Team members can start working on projects and requesting resources.</p>

<a href="{{appUrl}}/teams/{{teamId}}" class="button">View Team</a>

<p>Best regards,<br>
Incubation Management System Team</p>
